import React from 'react';
import {mount} from "enzyme";
import Group from "./group";
import {Header} from "./header";
import {Segment} from "./segment";
import {Button} from "./button";
 
describe("Grouped Items",()=>{
  const wrapper = mount(
    <Group>
      <Header>Header</Header>
      <Segment>Segment</Segment>
      <Button variation="secondary">Button</Button>
    </Group>
  );
 
  it("should match snapshot",()=>{
    expect(wrapper).toMatchSnapshot();
  });
 
  const groupComponent = wrapper.find('div').first();
 
  it("should container header with css class of attached top",()=>{
    const headerComponent = groupComponent.find('h1');
    expect(headerComponent).toHaveLength(1);
    expect(headerComponent.hasClass('ui')).toEqual(true);
    expect(headerComponent.hasClass('header')).toEqual(true);
    expect(headerComponent.hasClass('attached')).toEqual(true);
    expect(headerComponent.hasClass('top')).toEqual(true);
    expect(headerComponent.text()).toEqual('Header');
  });
 
  it("should container segment with css class of attached",()=>{
    const segmentComponent = groupComponent.find('div.segment');
    expect(segmentComponent).toHaveLength(1);
    expect(segmentComponent.hasClass('ui')).toEqual(true);
    expect(segmentComponent.hasClass('segment')).toEqual(true);
    expect(segmentComponent.hasClass('attached')).toEqual(true);
  });
 
  it("should container button with css class of attached bottom",()=>{
    const buttonComponent = groupComponent.find('button');
    expect(buttonComponent).toHaveLength(1);
    expect(buttonComponent.hasClass('aek-button')).toEqual(true);
    expect(buttonComponent.prop("className")).toMatch(/css-[a-z0-9]+-button-secondary-button/);
    expect(buttonComponent.hasClass('attached')).toEqual(true);
    expect(buttonComponent.hasClass('bottom')).toEqual(true);
  });
 
});
